## Prerequisites

Get Depot Tools and make sure it's in your path.
http://commondatastorage.googleapis.com/chrome-infra-docs/flat/depot_tools/docs/html/depot_tools_tutorial.html#_setting_up

And For linux:
sudo apt-get install libgtk-3-dev pkg-config ccache

## Build

./build.py # my wrapper around the gclient/gn/ninja

If that doesn't work try calling gn manually:

gn gen out/Debug --args='cc_wrapper="ccache" is_debug=true '
gn gen out/Default --args='cc_wrapper="ccache" '

Then build with ninja:

ninja -C out/Debug/ xhello # Build


## Debugging

gn args out/Default/ --list # List build args
gn args out/Default/ # Modify args in $EDITOR
